      <item>
        <title>Disc-based</title>
        <dc:creator><![CDATA[saivert]]></dc:creator>
        <description><![CDATA[
            <p>In order to efficiently load the game from optical media the team would have to restructure the game content. Similar to how things are stored on Console game discs. With optimizations made specially for the DVD format.</p>
<p>Just dumping the “for harddrive” content over on a disc wouldn’t work well.</p>
<p>tl;dr never gonna happen</p>
